Definition: a form of torture in which the hands are tied behind a person's back and they are lifted off the ground by a rope tied to their wrists, then allowed to drop until their fall is checked with a jerk by the rope
Synonyms: strapado, torture, a, form, of, in, which, the, hands, are, tied, behind, person, s, back, and, they, lifted, off, ground, by, rope, to, their, wrists, then, allowed, drop, until, fall, is, checked, with, jerk
Category: noun.act
